{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be dynamic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Design Studio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e53935 0%, #c62828 100%);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 4em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: -1px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        .hero-blob {\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -150px;\n            left: -100px;\n            width: 300px;\n            height: 300px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #c62828;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-top: 5px solid #e53935;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #e53935;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .cta {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c62828 0%, #b71c1c 100%);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #c62828;\n            padding: 15px 35px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: #fff;\n            border: 2px solid #fff;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 3em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .section h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .cta h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .btn {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n                padding: 12px 25px;\n            }\n        }\n        @keyframes pulsate {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 1; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }\n        }\n        .pulsating-element {\n            animation: pulsate 2s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-blob\"></div>\n        <h1>Apex Design Studio</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Digital Experiences That Captivate.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Web Design</h3>\n                    <p>Stunning, user-friendly websites that convert visitors into customers.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Branding & Identity</h3>\n                    <p>Creating memorable brand identities that resonate with your audience.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>\n                    <p>Intuitive and engaging interfaces for seamless user journeys.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h3>Digital Strategy</h3>\n                    <p>Data-driven strategies to elevate your online presence.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">We blend creativity with strategy to deliver bespoke design solutions. Our passion for innovation and commitment to client success makes us the ideal partner for your next project.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"cta\">\n            <h2>Ready to Elevate Your Brand?</h2>\n            <p>Let's create something extraordinary together.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn pulsating-element\">Get a Free Quote</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Design Studio. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple parallax effect for the hero blob\n        window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {\n            const heroBlob = document.querySelector('.hero-blob');\n            const scrollPosition = window.pageYOffset;\n            heroBlob.style.transform = `translateY(${scrollPosition * 0.5}px)`;\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}